intro: Shake and rotate your console to guide cubes into portals while navigating challenging obstacles! 30 levels offer hours of fun and challenging gameplay!
description:
This skill-based game puts your dexterity to the test. Cube movement is fully physics-based, and you control the world by simply rotating your console. The game uses the console’s built-in gyroscope and accelerometer to track your movements.

Each level features different obstacles, so every challenge feels fresh and unique.
